  <brief_title>A 6-Month Extension Study of OTO-104 in Meniere's Disease</brief_title>
  <official_title>A 6-Month, Multicenter, Phase 3, Open-Label Extension Safety Study of OTO-104 Given At 3-Month Intervals by Intratympanic Injection in Subjects With Unilateral Meniere's Disease</official_title>
  <sponsors>
