  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is an open-label extension study of a single intratympanic injection of OTO-104 given
      every 3 months for a total of 2 injections. Subjects must have completed either Otonomy study
      104-201403 (1-Year, Phase 2, Safety Study of OTO-104) or 104-201508 (Phase 3 Study of
      OTO-104) in order to be eligible for this open-label extension study.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
